title: Royals lose Game One of ALDS to Astros 5-2
text:
Royals lose Game One of ALDS to Astros 5-2 - News, Weather and Sports for Lincoln, NE; KLKNTV.com Member Center: Royals lose Game One of ALDS to Astros 5-2 
Posted By: Sports 
sports@klkntv.com 
The Houston Astros jumped out to a 3-0 lead and never looked back as they defeated the Kansas City Royals 5-2 Thursday night in Game One of the ALDS in Kansas City. The Astros hit a pair of solo homeruns, Kendrees Morales connected on two solo homeruns of his own. Game Two is Friday at 2:45 in Kansas City. All content Â© Copyright 2000 - 2015 WorldNow and KLKN.
